name: Gynoid: The Quest for Head
description: It's a platfomer. As a Gynoid (AKA Fembot) you are on a quest to find your head. But in it's place you can put tools,such as propelers and guns, for your quest! I wanted it to be a naked gynoid but...I had lots of plans, and this is as far as I got with them for the Lewd Gamejame. No excuses, here.
